text: Kwajalein Atoll High School is a secondary school in Kwajalein, Marshall Islands. It is a part of the Marshall Islands Public School System. The school serves the following atolls and islands: Kwajalein, Lae, Ujae, and Wotto."Annual Report 2011-2012." Ministry of Education (Marshall Islands). Retrieved on February 22, 2018. p. 54 (PDF p. 55/118). "Kwajalein Atoll High School enrolls students from Kwajalein and the Kabinmeto zone including schools in Ujae, Lae, and Wotto." ==References== Category:Schools in the Marshall Islands Category:Kwajalein Atoll Category:High schools
